Package fr.cnrs.iees.properties

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExtendablePropertyList
    A mutable SimplePropertyList, i.e. which can grow and shrink.
    PropertyListFactory  
    PropertyListGetters
    This interface isolates the generic getters for properties.
    PropertyListSetters
    This interface isolates the generic setters for properties.
    ReadOnlyPropertyList
    A read-only property list, ie with a size and getters but no setters.
    ResizeablePropertyList
    This interface contains the methods required to make a property list extendable.
    SimplePropertyList
    Simple, straightforward read-write property list for graph GraphElements.
    SimpleWriteProtectablePropertyList
    A property list for graph GraphElements that can be made read-only on demand.
